commitResults.messageTitle: Updated chatbot name and abstracted string logo to constants folder
commitResults.messageBody: Chatbot name updated to Billy. Logo design abstracted to a constant file that will contain all the design related string constants.

commitResults.messageTitle: Added Greet and Exit system messages
commitResults.messageBody: Private static methods for printing of the introduction and saying bye.

Billy.parseCommand(String userCmd) default action is to add to the String array containing the list.
If list is inputted, it will call Billy.list() to display the current list.

commitResults.messageTitle: Created Task class to facilitate the functions of a task.
commitResults.messageBody: This class represents a task and manages the done state of the tasks.

commitResults.messageTitle: Mark and unmark as done implemented for tasks.
commitResults.messageBody: Edited Billy.parseCommand() to allow for the parsing of marking and umarking of tasks.

commitResults.messageTitle: Implemented Todo, Deadline and Event classes that inherits from Task class.
Updated Billy.parseCommand() to receive todo, deadline and event commands.
commitResults.messageBody: Each command will parse the request and create the relevant Task childs.

commitResults.messageTitle: Setup test using the I/O redirection technique.
Added error handling for incorrect fields, unknown task number and unknown command.
commitResults.messageBody: 3 handled exception classes were created to handle the above errors. BillyUnknownException, BillyFieldErrorException and BillyUnknownTaskNumException.
Converted normal array used to store tasks to a ArrayList<Task>. Easily allows dynamic adding and removing of tasks from the list.
